{"about_the_game":"Are you ready for an epic adventure in Fright Knight Legend? You'll embark on a quest to save the cursed Kingdom of Brightmore, battling hordes of enemies and avoiding deadly traps to uncover scattered gems. But this is no ordinary tale - it's a story steeped in history, with heroes facing monsters believed lost to the ages.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140180/extras/PlayWithFriends-CoOpAction.png?t=1682615008\" /><br><br>Choose from three unique characters:<br><br>- Bella, a fierce female knight with lightning-quick combos<br>- Simon, a knight in shining armor who relies on pure strength to defeat his foes<br>- Merlin, a powerful magician with extra stamina for special attacks. <br><br>With up to three playable characters, each with their own attributes, you'll have a blast exploring the Kingdom of Brightmore.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140180/extras/FKL_Co-Op_v1-min.gif?t=1682615008\" /><br><br>You can choose between three heroes: <br><br>Bella, a female knight that has fists of fury, with quick combos<br>Simon, the Knight in shining armor that uses his strength to fight his way through the enemies<br>Merlin, the magician that has extra stamina for more special attacks<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140180/extras/600x280_Animated_Gif_IntroWizard.gif?t=1682615008\" /><br><br>Local co-op lets you team up with friends for even more fun, you can even play with friends remotely with Steam RemotePlay. And as you progress through your adventure, the legendary Wizard narrates your journey, adding an extra layer of excitement to the already thrilling gameplay.<br><br>If you're a fan of classic beat 'em ups like Streets of Rage, Final Fight, Shredder's Revenge, or Castle Crashers, then Fright Knight Legend is the adventure you've been wa